Tutoring.tutee set james bond 007007 egr222: will setup an account with james bond as the student name, 007007 as the student id, EGR222 as the class section
Tutoring.tutee hi: will get your custom sign-in link
Tutoring.tutee hi robbie: same as above, but overrides tutor's name with robbie
Tutoring.tutee hours 222: show the tutoring hours for EGR222
Tutoring.tutee join: will add you to the queue
Tutoring.tutee leave: will remove you from the queue
Tutoring.tutee room @student1 ... @studentN: makes a private room and invite everyone you mention to join
Tutoring.tutee: *commands with 222 can be replaced with 227 or 312*

Tutors.tutor start 222: set your tutoring session to EGR222
Tutors.tutor end: set your tutoring session to None
Tutors.tutor next: get the next student in the queue
Tutors.tutor stop: stop asking for the next student
Tutors.tutor move 1 3: move the student in position 1 to position 3 in the queue
Tutors.tutor swap 1 3: swaps the students in position 1 and position 3 in the queue
Tutors.tutor remove 3: removes the student in position 3 from the queue
Tutors.tutor clear: removes all students in your queue
Tutors.tutor: *commands with 222 can be replaced with 227 or 312*
